          "type": "custom_html",
          "name": "Size Chart",
          "settings": {
            "custom_html": "<style>\n    /* General container styling */\n    .size-chart-container {\n        width: 100%;\n        margin: 20px 0;\n    }\n    @media (min-width:768px)\n    {\n        .size-chart-container{\n            width: 100%;\n        }\n    }\n\n    /* * DROPDOWN STYLING \n     * Uses the <details> and <summary> tags for pure CSS toggle\n     */\n    details.size-chart-dropdown {\n        border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;\n        border-radius: 4px;\n        overflow: hidden;\n        transition: all 0.3s ease;\n    }\n\n    details.size-chart-dropdown[open] {\n        box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n    }\n\n    /* The \"Size Chart\" button style */\n    summary.size-chart-toggle {\n        background-color: #ffffff;\n        padding: 10px 20px;\n        cursor: pointer;\n        font-weight: 600;\n        color: #333;\n        list-style: none; /* Hides default triangle in some browsers */\n        display: flex;\n        justify-content: space-between;\n        align-items: center;\n        user-select: none;\n    }\n\n    /* Custom arrow icon */\n    summary.size-chart-toggle::after {\n        content: '+';\n        font-size: 18px;\n        font-weight: normal;\n    }\n\n    details[open] summary.size-chart-toggle::after {\n        content: '-';\n    }\n\n    /* Remove default marker for Webkit */\n    summary.size-chart-toggle::-webkit-details-marker {\n        display: none;\n    }\n\n    /* * TABLE STYLING \n     */\n    .size-chart-table {\n        width: 100%;\n        border-collapse: collapse;\n        text-align: center;\n        font-size: 15px;\n        background-color: #fff;\n        margin: 0\n    }\n    .size-chart-table th {\n        background-color: #fff;\n        color: #666;\n        font-weight: 600;\n        padding: 15px;\n        border-bottom: 2px solid #eee;\n        text-transform: uppercase;\n        font-size: 12px;\n        letter-spacing: 1px;\n    }\n\n    .size-chart-table td {\n        padding: 15px;\n        border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;\n        color: #333;\n        transition: background-color 0.2s ease;\n    }\n\n    /* * HOVER EFFECT \n     * When hovering a row (tr), change background color\n     */\n    .size-chart-table tbody tr:hover {\n        background-color: #f0f4f8; /* Light blue-grey highlight */\n        cursor: default;\n    }\n\n    /* Enhance the Size column text on hover */\n    .size-chart-table tbody tr:hover {\n        font-weight: bold;\n        color: #000;\n    }\n\n    /* Remove border from last row */\n    .size-chart-table tbody tr:last-child td {\n        border-bottom: none;\n    }\n    .size-chart-footer-img {\n        background-color: #fff;\n        padding: 15px;\n        text-align: center;\n        border-top: 1px solid #eee; /* Đường kẻ ngăn cách giữa bảng và ảnh */\n    }\n\n    .size-chart-footer-img img {\n        max-width: 100%; /* Đảm bảo ảnh không bị tràn ra ngoài trên mobile */\n        height: auto;\n        display: block;\n        margin: 0 auto;\n    }\n    /* ... Giữ nguyên các CSS cũ ... */\n\n    /* THÊM MỚI: Định dạng dòng lưu ý đơn vị đo */\n    .size-chart-note {\n        text-align: center;\n        font-size: 13px;\n        color: #666; /* Màu xám nhẹ cho tinh tế */\n        padding: 12px 0;\n        background-color: #fff;\n        border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;\n        font-style: italic;\n        letter-spacing: 0.5px;\n    }\n</style>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"size-chart-container\">\n    <details class=\"size-chart-dropdown\">\n        <summary class=\"size-chart-toggle\">📏 Size Chart</summary><div class=\"size-chart-note\">Unisex Fit • Measurements in Inches</div>\n<table class=\"size-chart-table\">\n            <thead>\n                <tr>\n                    <th>Size</th>\n                    <th>Length</th>\n                    <th>Width</th>\n                    <th>Sleeve</th>\n                </tr>\n            </thead>\n            <tbody>\n                <tr>\n                    <td>S</td>\n                    <td>20</td>\n                    <td>17</td>\n                    <td>17</td>\n                </tr>\n                <tr>\n                    <td>M</td>\n                    <td>22</td>\n                    <td>17.5</td>\n                    <td>18</td>\n                </tr>\n                <tr>\n                    <td>L</td>\n                    <td>23</td>\n                    <td>18.5</td>\n                    <td>20.5</td>\n                </tr>\n                <tr>\n                    <td>XL</td>\n                    <td>24.5</td>\n                    <td>20.5</td>\n                    <td>23</td>\n                </tr>               \n            </tbody>\n        </table>\n        <div class=\"size-chart-footer-img\">\n            <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0740/5879/3017/files/size_guide_sweatshirt_gildan.jpg?v=1770192532\" alt=\"Measurement Guide\">\n        </div>\n    </details>\n</div>"
