        "text_HNUwVy": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "collapse": true,
            "title": "Can I personalize the designs with my own text?",
            "icon": "none",
            "header_image_width": 50,
            "faq_answer": "<p>Yes, absolutely! Many of our products are designed for customization. You can add names, special dates, or meaningful messages in the designated fields on the product page to create a truly one-of-a-kind gift.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "image_width": 465,
            "liquid": "",
            "html": "",
            "show_contact_form": false
          }
        },
        "text_piKEyj": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "collapse": true,
            "title": "How long will it take to receive my order?",
            "icon": "none",
            "header_image_width": 50,
            "faq_answer": "<p>Since our items are made-to-order, please allow <strong>1-2 business days</strong> for production. Once shipped, delivery time depends on the option you choose: <strong>Standard (3–4 business days)</strong> or <strong>Economy (5–8 business days)</strong>.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "image_width": 465,
            "liquid": "",
            "html": "",
            "show_contact_form": false
          }
        },
        "text_jUkK9m": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "collapse": true,
            "title": "How do I choose the right size for apparel?",
            "icon": "none",
            "header_image_width": 50,
            "faq_answer": "<p>We recommend checking our <strong>Size Chart</strong> located on each product page before placing an order. Our apparel is true-to-size, but if you prefer a looser fit, we suggest ordering one size up.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "image_width": 465,
            "liquid": "",
            "html": "",
            "show_contact_form": false
          }
        },
        "text_mC9ejN": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "collapse": true,
            "title": "What is your return and exchange policy?",
            "icon": "none",
            "header_image_width": 50,
            "faq_answer": "<p>We stand behind the quality of our products. If your item arrives damaged, defective, or with a printing error, please contact our support team within <strong>7 days</strong> of delivery. We will happily arrange a free replacement or a full refund for you.</p><p>Visit: <a href=\"/pages/policy\" title=\"POLICY\">Policy Page</a> to learn more.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "image_width": 465,
            "liquid": "",
            "html": "",
            "show_contact_form": false
          }
        }
      },
